    "name": "MOTHERSHIP",
    "steam_appid": 1818290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/3a895ffe6bed3c211d2ad8c5bcaf79cd.webp?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=21 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live an interstellar voyage through space and time, from youth to old age, from planet Earth to the edge of the galaxy, from complete loneliness to being reunited with your loved ones. You are a forgotten child who will travel across the real star systems of our galaxy looking for other space refugees like you, to live in peace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/6ae47c26793132189fe532c135fc1c70.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/6ae47c26793132189fe532c135fc1c70.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/6ae47c26793132189fe532c135fc1c70.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/23eef42fa09f7b1305c46a277d6e170b.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/23eef42fa09f7b1305c46a277d6e170b.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/23eef42fa09f7b1305c46a277d6e170b.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ ​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/da6031193afc92be62c88837259e1813.webp?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=21 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track the signals of the Motherships, the huge spaceships humans used to escape Earth during a massive exodus. ​However, outer space is not merciful. If you reach a Mothership that didn't survive, salvage its core and use its fuel to continue searching deeper into space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/85447aeb46c253277f4f9ae924699fc9.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/85447aeb46c253277f4f9ae924699fc9.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/85447aeb46c253277f4f9ae924699fc9.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/cceed50a2d517b531f2e4c678acdfc7b.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/cceed50a2d517b531f2e4c678acdfc7b.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/cceed50a2d517b531f2e4c678acdfc7b.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/9927aa59a10def1b8090d03ec604c99b.webp?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=21 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your compass radar and your observational skills to find your own way to the cores across asteroid fields, exotic planets and Mothership wrecks. You will have the equipment you need to endure hazardous environments and to open new shortcuts in your path. Learn and adapt to different gravities, natural dangers and even catastrophic events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/68f56137c76e9b0ad9539e97383debf1.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/68f56137c76e9b0ad9539e97383debf1.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/68f56137c76e9b0ad9539e97383debf1.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/9770a9d8cd24db1015ab54cd88a96558.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/9770a9d8cd24db1015ab54cd88a96558.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/9770a9d8cd24db1015ab54cd88a96558.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/b3b52c6f85921c303fcb8eef9056aaa5.webp?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=21 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the calm and the thrill of zero gravity. Learn to navigate in weightlessness with a pair of rocket boots, where every impulse counts, or take a break and drift, watching the universe pass by from the safety of your ship's cupola.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/ee776747a25bb30f3b9382452329bbad.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/ee776747a25bb30f3b9382452329bbad.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/ee776747a25bb30f3b9382452329bbad.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/7a7babf349b8487e51a5eb7789365750.poster.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/7a7babf349b8487e51a5eb7789365750.webm?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/7a7babf349b8487e51a5eb7789365750.mp4?t=1772202922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I hope you'll enjoy it :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carlos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818290/extras/9b81adfd3c270a29c721465670b0cadf.avif?t=1772202922\" width=616 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">​ </p>",
